completionOptions.mergeCommitMessage:
Merged PR 702: Permission for A400M CoreAll Database

In Cockpit user can access the A400MCoreAll database if user have the permission. We implement this feature in last PI. 
So while selecting the datasource if user have permission he can access A400M database. 
But if your share his dashboard to another user who doesn't have A400M database permission still that user able to see dashboard. 

**In this story we implement security while loading the dashboard. If user have the permission on A400M database then only he can access the dashboard.**

**_Note: Please delete the branch after merge._
